task.summary: Improved some of the analysis logic. Now supports identification and decoding of ascii hex encoded values.
Decoded values fix. and a few other minor changes. :)
Fixed decoded field in table. Added "Deflected".
Fixed multiple format detection, including issue #2, issue #3
Fixed some of the analyzer logic to make it work a bit better.
Added export button to export to csv file.
Cleaned up formatting of cookie statistics table.
Added support for basic JSON objects. (lists not handled... yet)
Improved some of the pattern matching.
Skip reflection check for values less than 3 characters.
Change default to ignore empty values.
Added skeleton for deep analysis functionality.
Added popup menu to send request to Repeater.
Added a close button for session analysis tabs.
Open correct tab when sending to Paramalyzer
Uniform horizontal sizing of detail pane columns.
Put Deep Analysis tab close button in the same place as the session analysis tab.
Added Type, Domains, and Paths to the Cookie Analysis Tab.
Fixed quirky looking session help tab in dark mode.
